{{!
    @template tool_fix_delete_modules/report_table

    The template displays a table which forms part of a report about one course_delete_module task.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * title string - The title of the moodle database and the adhoc task's taskid and related course module id(s).
    * table string - HTML table listing records from a particular moodle database table related to the course_delete_module task.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "title": "course_modules taskid(4321) (cmid:5432, instanceid: 1342)",
        "table": "<table><tr><td> ....</td></tr></table>",
    }
}}
<div class="fix-report-table">
    <h5 class="fix-report-table-heading">{{title}}</h5>
    {{{table}}}
</div>
